{
  "stem": "23096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But evidently, even though this was just a labor camp where they were systematically starving the people to death-- which is a, a more horrible form of death than putting them in a gas chamber like they did in Auschwitz-- that they were trying to hide some of these bodies.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were actually digging up, pulling bodies out of these mass graves and trying to burn them before the, the Americans and-- or whoever got there, got there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were signs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They had brought ovens and stuff in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Some places, there were just piles of bodies, like on railroad ties-- not ties, no, the rails, iron rails, make, like, a grill and piled the bodies up on that and burning them that way.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were-- there were-- anywhere you went, there were bodies all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There were some [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] buildings that they were, like, using them for-- they weren't really barracks because they weren't that type of building.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was more like a, a cow barn with a big door on one end and a big door on the other and with an aisle down the center.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And most of them had bunks in them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we went through them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there weren't too many living people left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But the ones that were laying in their bunks, then they, they, they just stare at you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[MOANS] It's-- it-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's hard to describe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That's why I think the pictures and stuff are so important.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were a lot of dead bodies in there that, you know, they had taken out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So maybe some of these dead-- or the ones that were still alive they thought were dead and just left them.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
